# Per-Dockerfile ignore (BuildKit) — paths are relative to the build context
# root (the workspace dir holding kai-cli/ kai-core/ kai-engine/). Keep the
# context to just the three Go modules; drop everything heavy/irrelevant.
*
!kai-cli/
!kai-core/
!kai-engine/
# Prune non-source weight from the three modules.
**/.git
**/node_modules
**/testdata
**/*_test.go
kai-cli/deploy/kai-ci/build.sh
